27
00:01:19,041 --> 00:01:20,333
Yeah.

28
00:01:20,416 --> 00:01:22,125
There's gotta be some adults
who can't drink coffee.

29
00:01:22,208 --> 00:01:24,083
You know you're a kid right?

30
00:01:24,166 --> 00:01:25,000
[gasps]

31
00:01:25,083 --> 00:01:27,375
Why're you so mean?

32
00:01:27,458 --> 00:01:28,333
Ahh!

33
00:01:28,416 --> 00:01:30,958
Ahhh! Ow!

34
00:01:33,458 --> 00:01:35,416
Oh great.

35
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:38,250
Adults don't try to tackle
their friends, Mina.

36
00:03:20,125 --> 00:03:21,541
[NISHIKATA]
As I've come to expect,

37
00:03:21,625 --> 00:03:25,083
Takagi made fun
of me a ton today.

38
00:03:25,166 --> 00:03:26,750
[groans]

39
00:03:33,083 --> 00:03:35,083
[NISHIKATA]
But I'll get her tomorrow!

40
00:03:35,166 --> 00:03:36,625
[TAKAGI]
Nishikata.

41
00:03:37,916 --> 00:03:39,500
[NISHIKATA]
Takagi!

42
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:42,041
Oh.

43
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,958
On your own today?

44
00:03:44,041 --> 00:03:44,875
[NISHIKATA]
Yeah.

45
00:03:44,958 --> 00:03:46,958
Cool. Let's walk home together.

46
00:03:47,041 --> 00:03:49,500
Uh. Wait, why?

47
00:03:50,958 --> 00:03:51,500
[TAKAGI]
What?

48
00:03:51,583 --> 00:03:52,583
Um, sorry.

49
00:03:52,666 --> 00:03:54,333
I thought I heard something.

50
00:03:54,416 --> 00:03:57,041
But, um, you're
on your bike, and all.

51
00:03:57,125 --> 00:03:58,708
[TAKAGI]
I'll just push.

52
00:04:01,375 --> 00:04:02,750
[NISHIKATA]
"Empty Can."

53
00:04:07,583 --> 00:04:09,958
That's that new drink
that just came out, isn't it?

54
00:04:10,041 --> 00:04:11,833
Is it good?

55
00:04:11,916 --> 00:04:13,416
[NISHIKATA]
What is this?

56
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,375
Some kind of trap?

57
00:04:15,458 --> 00:04:16,833
I like it.

58
00:04:16,916 --> 00:04:18,458
You wanna have a sip?

59
00:04:18,541 --> 00:04:19,333
Can I?

60
00:04:19,416 --> 00:04:21,416
[NISHIKATA]
Mm-hmm.

61
00:04:22,541 --> 00:04:24,250
Great. Thank you.

62
00:04:26,166 --> 00:04:27,583
Not that I really mind,

63
00:04:27,666 --> 00:04:32,166
