70
00:04:46,166 --> 00:04:47,333
Ahh...

71
00:04:47,416 --> 00:04:48,750
Boy, that was good.

72
00:04:48,833 --> 00:04:50,458
Thanks again.

73
00:04:58,666 --> 00:05:00,916
Can't drink it?

74
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:03,750
No. Of course I can drink it.

75
00:05:04,125 --> 00:05:05,416
[NISHIKATA]
It's nothing.

76
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:07,458
No big deal.

77
00:05:11,291 --> 00:05:12,791
It's like an indirect kiss.

78
00:05:12,875 --> 00:05:14,291
Aah!

79
00:05:18,583 --> 00:05:21,333
[TAKAGI laughs]
You're so jumpy.

80
00:05:22,416 --> 00:05:26,333
[NISHIKATA] There's gotta
be a trash can around here.

81
00:05:26,416 --> 00:05:28,958
Man!

82
00:05:29,041 --> 00:05:30,125
Wow!

83
00:05:30,208 --> 00:05:32,791
That was a pretty
good shot, Nishikata.

84
00:05:32,875 --> 00:05:34,583
